files are stored in working directory

```{r}
URL <- "https://www.dropbox.com/s/aawh33hneqru6j9/metazoan_COI_marine_v3.zip?dl=1"
download.file(URL, destfile = "metazoan_COI_marine_v3.zip", mode = "wb")
