# Tips for browsing the GitHub CSL Style Repository:  https://github.com/citation-style-language/styles
# To quickly search the styles in the GitHub CSL style repository by file name, go to URL https://github.com/citation-style-language/styles, and press t to activate GitHubs File Finder and start typing. E.g. type "ecology", and one of the surfaced options will be "ecology-letters"
# use this filename in the style = "" option

